---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Next.js for Enterprise Applications | React Framework Guide"
  description="Next.js enterprise application development for banking and finance. Real implementation from MONETA Auto onboarding suite."
>
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-12">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="text-sm text-slate-400">
      <a href="/" class="transition hover:text-accent">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">→</span>
      <a href="/vocabulary" class="transition hover:text-accent">Vocabulary</a>
      <span class="mx-2">→</span>
      <span class="text-slate-200">Next.js Enterprise</span>
    </nav>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <p class="eyebrow">Frameworks</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white sm:text-5xl">Next.js for Enterprise</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">React framework with SSR, SSG, and API routes</p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[32px] border border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent p-8 shadow-card">
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-100">
        <strong class="text-white">Definition:</strong> Next.js is a React framework providing server-side rendering, static generation, API routes, and built-in optimizations for building enterprise-grade web applications.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-card space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Enterprise Use Cases</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-200">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Admin dashboards:</strong> SSR for fast initial load</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Customer portals:</strong> SEO and performance optimized</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Internal tools:</strong> Hybrid static and dynamic pages</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Marketing sites:</strong> API integrations with SSG</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-card space-y-6">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow text-accent">Case Study</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Real Project: MONETA Auto</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-200">
        Built the <strong class="text-white">MONETA Auto onboarding suite</strong> with Next.js + React Hook Form for automotive finance loan processing, handling complex multi-step validations and REST integrations.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Related Vocabulary</h3>
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <a href="/vocabulary/react-typescript" class="grid-panel">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-accent">React TypeScript</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Type-safe Next.js development</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/vocabulary/react-hook-form" class="grid-panel">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-accent">React Hook Form</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Form handling in MONETA Auto</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[32px] border border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent p-8 text-center shadow-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Need Next.js Development?</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-slate-200">I've built enterprise Next.js applications for banking and finance sectors.</p>
      <a href="mailto:marekdolnicek@gmail.com" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-full bg-accent px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-ink shadow-card transition hover:bg-accentMuted">Let's talk</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
